        "content": "<p>cfallin submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/13077#pullrequestreview-4101706784\">PR review</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This looks reasonable overall -- with my level of review on all of the output-parsing cod calibrated at \"this is a useful tool for developers\" rather than \"production-ready robustness\".</p>\n<p>A thought below but otherwise I'm happy to see this in-tree for its usefulness. Thanks!</p>\n</blockquote>",
